{"tid":2045213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇下南非點搞抗爭","createTime":"2020-05-31T15:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T18:08:09.000Z","uid":153938,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62c09a4f105967fbfff69477558e2c2c1f4888d3","tid":2045213,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"雖然美國成日制裁人，但好似香港咁\u001d<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">主動攬炒\u001d</span></span></strong>嘅例子真係唔多。<br />\n不過又唔係冇例子，果個就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">南非</span></span>（呢排成日講嘢嗰個<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">曼德拉</span></span></strong>嘅屋企啊）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n長文可能會冇心機睇，所以我整咗條片，<br />\n講下人哋點搞<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">南非\u001d經濟圈</span></strong>，<br />\n點樣由<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">畀人拉去坐監</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">畀人射死</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">畀人立法禁止搞社運</span></span></strong>，去到收政府皮。<br />\n<br />\n學藝未精，各位巴絲賞下面：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">【南非如何被制裁】</span><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買如何對抗政權？南非反種族隔離之路</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IW7R07VnkB4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIW7R07VnkB4&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=0ac30e3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IW7R07VnkB4</a>"},{"pid":"9e833ce9307099218b7edf1c3c8eebe1b007b381","tid":2045213,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:57:50.000Z","msg":"睇完有興趣，可以討論下有咩可以參考"},{"pid":"8fd04f38daabde50a4469463cd457fd6ec589b17","tid":2045213,"uid":153938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"南非抗爭有<strong>